<section id="idg-cmmoperator-cmmoperator-install-c-cmmoinstlogagent-xml-1">
 <title>Installing the Log Agent</title>
 <para>
  For monitoring <phrase>CMM</phrase>, a Log Agent must be installed on your
  <phrase>CMM</phrase> host.
 </para>
 <para>
  As a prerequisite for installing the agent, the offline resources, the
  OpenStack extensions, and the Monitoring Service must have been installed.
 </para>
 <para>
  The installation consists of the following steps:
 </para>
 <orderedlist>
  <listitem>
   <para>
    Installing the agent.
   </para>
  </listitem>
  <listitem>
   <para>
    Configuring the agent.
   </para>
  </listitem>
 </orderedlist>
